#~ msgid ""
#~ "&kappname; can be played online on any GGZ Gaming Zone site. You can find "
#~ "other players there, and compete against them. Just enter one of the "
#~ "available Reversi rooms with any GGZ core client, such as kggz, and "
#~ "&kappname; will be offered to you as your favourite game client. If a GGZ "
#~ "core client is installed, you can try out GGZ by visiting the <ulink url="
#~ "\"ggz://live.ggzgamingzone.org/#Reversi\">community site</ulink>."
#~ msgstr ""
